name: The Last Hole Cutter
description:
Years ago, the donut and bagel lands lived together in harmony. but everything changed when the holy dough cutter disappeared

To play user the Keyboard:  

  • Left + Right  to move
  • Space to flay
  • Use the mouse to point and shoot.
